Name: Datarecovery.com MK
AboutMe:
Datarecovery.com is a world leader in data recovery providing recovery services for single drives, RAID systems, SAN, SSD, Flash Media, Mac/Apple products, and mobile devices. We also offer Computer Forensics services, as well as Tape Duplication and Recovery.

Datarecovery.com formed in 1998 originally as ESS Data Recovery, and incorporated in 1999. As one of the first data recovery companies in the world, Datarecovery.com has developed technology used in every major data recovery laboratory and has consistently researched and implemented new data recovery methods and techniques. With four full-service labs, and growing, Datarecovery.com services thousands of clients worldwide.
